{"title":"世上无难事　只要敢登攀——献给登山队的歌","authors":["向明"],"dates":[{"year":1975,"month":6,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上无难事　只要敢登攀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给登山队的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京的红色电波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把激动人心的喜讯频传："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜艳的五星红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一次在地球之巅飘展！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝贺你们呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀登珠穆朗玛的英雄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你们致敬呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的突击队员！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仿佛看见："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭一颗红心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两只铁脚板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战十级风暴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏万丈冰山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首战斗的诗篇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲进军的鼓点！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仿佛听见："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用亲身的斗争实践，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借万里风雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传壮语豪言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上无难事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要敢登攀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上无难事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要敢登攀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为巩固无产阶级专政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民正勇攀理论高山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政治夜校里明灯闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农兵手捧《共产党宣言》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学你们不畏道路崎岖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心攀登光辉的顶点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上无难事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要敢登攀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为巩固无产阶级专政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级快马加鞭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个生产指标的红箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突破历史的水平线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追着你们的脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射向更高的峰巅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上无难事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要敢登攀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为巩固无产阶级专政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业战线在大干快干！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看一处处人造海人造平原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨红花开遍塞北岭南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农发出豪迈誓言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定叫粮堆如山峰高耸蓝天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上无难事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要敢登攀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为巩固无产阶级专政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命战士满怀仇恨把兵练。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习你们敢于胜利的英雄气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"概，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底批判帝修反的谰言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵略者胆敢来侵犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定叫它人仰马翻有来无还！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}